videos.description: Wolverines FB Ben Mason hustles into the end zone to get Michigan on the board.
videos.headline: Mason opens up Michigan scoring

videos.description: Nebraska's Jaron Woodyard runs into Michigan's Donovan Peoples-Jones after Peoples-Jones called for the fair catch.
videos.headline: Peoples-Jones gets taken out on the fair catch

videos.description: Michigan's Karan Higdon goes practically untouched 44 yards into the end zone for another Wolverine touchdown.
videos.headline: Higdon flies for the 44-yd Michigan TD

videos.description: Ben Mason runs for the 4-yard touchdown to put Michigan up 20-0 in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Mason gets his second TD of the day

videos.description: Shea Patterson finds Zach Gentry wide open in the end zone to put Michigan up 30-0 in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Patterson's pass TD widens Michigan lead

videos.description: Ben Mason runs in for the 1 yard Michigan touchdown, his third of the game, putting the Wolverines up 37-0.
videos.headline: Michigan's Mason gets his 3rd TD of the game

videos.description: QB Dylan McCaffrey throws a dime to WR Ronnie Bell for a 56-yard Wolverine touchdown
videos.headline: Michigan's McCaffrey connects with Bell for a 56-yard TD
